Author: babyfaced-bitch
Text: I’m super ashamed of it yeah. I don’t want anyone to know because I’ll feel like more of a burden to everyone. Which makes me feel like shit because I feel like I’m lying to everyone. Which makes me feel even more like shit lol. I just want to be as good as everyone wants me to be or thinks I am. I just want to be good, that’s all.

Author: boring-coffee
Text: Yeah, I pretty much always feel ashamed of my ED. Which in turn makes my ED worse because of how awful I feel lol.
